            "title": "全日收市｜港股午後高位徘徊   金礦及濠賭股升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後高位徘徊，不超過上午波幅，金礦股、濠賭股上揚，紫金(02899)創歷史新高，科網股為升市動力，汽車股弱。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報25829，升490點或1.94%，今早高開25606點，升267點或1.06%，最低見25590，升251點或0.99%，升幅持續擴大，最高見25918，飛升579點或2.29%，午後波幅不超過上午區間。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">紫金礦業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240909_FI_source-web_sands_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240909_FI_source-web_sands_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：金沙中國官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_00175-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_00175-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：吉利汽車官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250724_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250724_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20240318_FI_source-ap_港股.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">紫金礦業官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240909_FI_source-web_sands_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：金沙中國官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_00175-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：吉利汽車官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250724_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日升177點或3.14%，報5825，今早開報5731點，升84點或1.49%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日升168點或1.85%，報9248點，今早以9176點開市，升97點或1.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指升512點或2.02%，報25893，高水27點 ; 科指期貨升198點或3.51%，報5837，高水12點 ; 國指期升178點或1.96%，報9260，高水12點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">全日成交3696.98億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國聯儲局鮑威爾放鴿，亞洲股市普遍升。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美元下跌，金礦股向上，紫金礦業(02899)收升6.38%，報24.34元，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 最高見24.58元，升7.43%，為歷史高位。中國黃金國際(02099)升4.95%，報89.05元 ; 靈寶(03330)升5.21%，報22.52元 ; 潼關黃金(00340)升4.32%，報1.93元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科技股升，網易(09999)午後造好，收升6.04%，報219.4元 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)升5.51%，報124.5元，成交居首，貢獻恒指107點 ; 騰訊(00700)升2.42%，至614.5元，貢獻恒指158點 ; 美團(03690)升3.29%，報122.3元，貢獻恒指33點，三股成撐市主力。百度(09888)升6.25%，報91元 ; 快手(01024)升5.14%，報78.75元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">午後濠賭股升，金沙中國(01928)升5.22%，報11.28元 ; 銀河娛樂(00027)升5.59%，報42.32元 ; 永利澳門(01128)升5.41%，報7.01元 ; 美高梅中國(02282)升4.59%，報15.95元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240909_FI_source-web_sands_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240909_FI_source-web_sands_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：金沙中國官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內房股及物管股繼續有追捧，龍湖(00960)升5.22%，造11.28元，暫為最強藍籌；中國海外(00688)升1.26%，報14.44元；華潤置地(01109)升0.95%，造31.76元；華潤萬象生活(01209)升4.12%，造41.94元；中海宏洋(00081)績後揚6.98%，造2.3元；保利物業(06049)績後升2.63%，報37.4元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">吉利汽車(00175)跑輸，跌1.35%，報19.71元 ; 東方海外(00316)跌0.88%，報146.1元 ; 比亞迪電子(00285)跌0.81%，報39.18元，為表現最差三藍籌股。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_00175-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_00175-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：吉利汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東風集團(00489)，分派附屬新能源汽車公司嵐圖汽車香港上市，集團本身將私有化，復牌飛升，最終收升54.1%，報9.2元，入20大成交額。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指新貴升，泡泡瑪特(09992)升1.94%，報326.6元 ; 京東物流(02618)飆7.39%，報13.95元 ; 中電信(00728)升0.81%，報6.23元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250724_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250724_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15203590-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e5%be%98%e5%be%8a-%e9%87%91%e7%a4%a6%e5%8f%8a%e6%bf%a0%e8%b3%ad%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87",
